1. DEFINITIONS

"Software" means the MuseDock Panel source code, documentation, and
associated files in this repository.

"Operator Use" means operating the Software to manage your own
infrastructure and services, including paid hosting operations for your
own customers (for example: domains, websites, databases, mail and
server administration run by your organization).

"Software Resale" means selling, sublicensing, relicensing, white-labeling
or redistributing the Software itself (source or binaries) as a product.

"Managed Panel SaaS" means offering access to the Software itself as a
standalone panel product/service to third parties where the panel is the
core commercial offering.

"Portal Module" means MuseDock Portal and customer-facing modules/features
explicitly marked as requiring a separate commercial license key.

